    "AL reduces uncertainty by adding new data to the training set.",
    "AL has traditionally been used to improve model predictions, but is now also used to explore the chemical space.",
    "It identifies and investigates molecules linked with high uncertainty, assumed to be those presenting less-explored molecular structures.",
    "By doing so, AL enables more efficient exploration with fewer experiments.",
    "These approaches employ AI techniques like Bayesian machine learning algorithms and Ensemble learning to estimate uncertainty."
